The '''long-barreled blaster''' was among the [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] weapons wielded by [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] troopers at the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]].

==Behind the scenes==
Nothing is known about this blaster model from ''The Empire Strikes Back''. It does not visually match a [[Mark II medium repeating blaster cannon|Merr-Sonn Mark II]] or [[BlasTech light repeating blaster|Blastech Light Repeating Blaster]]. The long-barreled blaster shows up a few times in the Battle of Hoth scenes.

